{"tid":2337652,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"今天不小心把元朗的市民打傷了","createTime":"2020-12-23T12:19:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T01:23:47.000Z","uid":10503,"like":91,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"08f0ec0b89f6f06178b0f379f5a46ea53d6f18a4","tid":2337652,"uid":10503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T12:19:44.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"large\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VzhCOZd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVzhCOZd.jpg&h=b74472cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今天不小心把元朗的市民打傷了 <br />\n事後我用了三十九分鐘去到達現場<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/COzJKxC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCOzJKxC.jpg&h=82325206&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n發現打碎了的頭蓋骨 <br />\n竟然比起平日那個形態更美<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KWaAAEm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKWaAAEm.jpg&h=25643019&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n然後我再用了十分鐘去恐嚇記者 <br />\n再為其抄牌<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qp8eRd2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQp8eRd2.png&h=60f342f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這短短的九十分鐘 <br />\n算是今天我思緒最興奮的時間<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K8wj2jK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK8wj2jK.jpg&h=355067c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n打傷了的市民 <br />\n是我今天看過最美好的東西<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3WRW4yH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3WRW4yH.jpg&h=b055663e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而那記者著地的那一聲 <br />\n是聽過最美好的聲音 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ne3VAFT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fne3VAFT.jpg&h=ff041f80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原來人生覺得最無恥的事情 <br />\n也未必是最心寒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0TR0MOh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0TR0MOh.png&h=db8dd1d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n因為最心寒的 <br />\n可能一直就在眼前而未曾發現 <br />\n又或者根本就是自己 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/evyynk2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fevyynk2.jpg&h=adad5e6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我想我找到了答案</span></strong>"},{"pid":"75e8088497049210627b95d9d956fb213e0b4d37","tid":2337652,"uid":106290,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T12:21:25.000Z","msg":"中國豪死全家"},{"pid":"59f088cdc545dfab06ee109475b843391e576ddb","tid":2337652,"uid":285514,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T12:22:03.000Z","msg":"高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fed622d9a0dff5941331bd9b4f20b5ea84c525d","tid":2337652,"uid":10503,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T12:26:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5R5wTwM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5R5wTwM.png&h=a3b64d53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/16CiwPChpr0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F16CiwPChpr0&d=djscsuFvXcghIMf2lgFVpycuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=29f98ae4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/16CiwPChpr0</a>"},{"pid":"13eb02eb58a1354b8cf09d540a48eaa7bbd2153e","tid":2337652,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T12:26:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2c1d3781696054502916b6eb68b374cdeb4a31a8","tid":2337652,"uid":10503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T12:27:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eea9cee8e471fe5600cbe5db559a707dc906a15","tid":2337652,"uid":24788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T12:28:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be